sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor FD as Front Desk Staff
    participant UI as Occupancy Page<br/>(/occupancy/page.tsx)
    participant Dialog as CheckoutDialog
    participant Action as adminFetchCheckoutData
    participant SB as Supabase Client
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant RT as Supabase Realtime
    participant HKAPI as /api/housekeeping/<br/>checkout-cleaning

    FD->>UI: Klik kamar dengan status 'checked-in'
    UI->>Dialog: open CheckoutDialog

    Dialog->>Action: adminFetchCheckoutData(roomId)
    Action->>DB: SELECT reservation +<br/>billing_items WHERE status='pending'
    DB-->>Action: { reservation, unpaidBills }
    Action-->>Dialog: data
    Dialog-->>FD: Tampilkan ringkasan + bills

    alt Reservasi overdue (lewat tanggal checkout)
        Dialog->>Dialog: hitung daysLate
        Dialog->>SB: INSERT billing_items<br/>(category='late_fee',<br/>quantity=daysLate,<br/>total_price=daysLate*roomRate)
        SB->>DB: INSERT
        Dialog->>Dialog: refresh checkout data
        Dialog-->>FD: Show late fee added,<br/>minta lanjut bayar
    end

    alt Ada unpaid bills
        FD->>Dialog: Pilih payment method
        Dialog->>Dialog: processCheckoutPayment(method, amount)
        Dialog->>SB: INSERT payments<br/>(amount, method, txId)
        SB->>DB: INSERT
        DB-->>SB: payment row

        Dialog->>SB: UPDATE billing_items<br/>SET status='paid'<br/>WHERE id IN (unpaidBillIds)
        SB->>DB: UPDATE
    end

    Dialog->>SB: UPDATE reservations<br/>SET status='checked-out',<br/>actual_check_out=NOW()
    SB->>DB: UPDATE
    DB->>RT: emit postgres_changes

    Dialog->>SB: UPDATE rooms<br/>SET status='cleaning'
    SB->>DB: UPDATE
    DB->>RT: emit postgres_changes

    Dialog->>Dialog: createCheckoutInvoice(paymentResult)
    Dialog->>SB: INSERT invoices<br/>(reservation_id, invoice_number,<br/>subtotal, total_amount,<br/>payment_method, status='paid')
    SB->>DB: INSERT
    DB-->>SB: invoice row

    Dialog->>Dialog: setCheckoutInvoice(invoice)<br/>setCheckoutSuccess(true)

    Note over Dialog,HKAPI: Trigger housekeeping task otomatis<br/>(via background job atau<br/>dipicu manual via tab Housekeeping)

    Dialog-->>FD: Tampilkan invoice success<br/>+ Print button

    FD->>Dialog: Klik "Print Checkout Invoice"
    Dialog->>Dialog: printCheckoutInvoice()<br/>window.print()

    RT-->>UI: realtime sync
    UI->>UI: Update kalender + KPI
    UI-->>FD: Kamar berubah ke 'cleaning',<br/>siap untuk housekeeping
